splash.splashContent:
CONDITIONS OF USE (Please Read Carefully)

EFFECTIVE DATE: 7/8/2021

The Hawaii Cesspool Prioritization Tool (HCPT) was developed by the University of Hawaii (UH) in collaboration with the state of Hawaii Department of Health Wastewater Branch (DOH), and is provided as an informational service to the public. Users are responsible for understanding the background/limitations of the tool and evaluating the appropriateness of the tool for their objectives.

Although the HCPT has been developed with the most recent and best available data, errors may be present. UH and DOH is not responsible for any resulting errors and reserves the right to update the web interface as needed pursuant to further analysis and review. No warranty, expressed or implied, is made by UH, DOH, or the State of Hawaii as to the functionality of the web interface and related material, nor shall the fact of release constitute any such warranty.

Furthermore, the HCPT is released on condition that neither UH, DOH, nor State of Hawaii shall be held liable for any damages resulting from its authorized or unauthorized use.

All content and results are in the public domain and may be used freely, with appropriate credit given to the authors. Suggested citation: Mezzacapo, M., Shuler, C., Renteria, A., Allen, K. Whittier, R. 2021. The Hawaii Cesspool Prioritization Tool, website: http://.

By using the tool you agree to the above terms and conditions.
